1. npm create vite@latest | choose react and typescript
2. Install dependences as you see in package.json
3. Delete all existing codes from vite react | Like App.tsx contents, App.css file, index.css contents
4. Configure vite.config.ts file | Like using @component/filename.ext on importing files/components
5. Configure tsconfig.json file | to accept paths
6. Install taiwlind extensions and tailwind for vite react
7. Install prettier and prettier tailwind | Create prettier config file
8. Update tailwind.config.js to add custom classes for css
9. 

A fitness web page project mainly built using React, Typescript, Tailwind CSS. 
Tech stacks: React, Vite, Typescript, Tailwind